    <summary>Shows webcam image on desktop</summary>
    <description>
        <p>Show your webcam image on your desktop for presentations or screencasts.</p>
        <p>Usage:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Start MyHumbleSelf</li>
            <li>Resize the window and move it to the desired location</li>
            <li>Set to "always on top" via your window manager (right click on titlebar)</li>
            <li>Hover the webcam image and click the "eye"-button in top right to hide window
                controls</li>
        </ol>
        <p>Some notable features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Use face tracking to keep your head in center</li>
            <li>Choose among various shape-masks to add some style</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Tags: webcam, presentations, screencast</p>
    </description>
